moji\" />, 仲要大家支持)<br />\n<br />\n第五期民調結果POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1726268/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1726268/page/1</a> <span style=\"color: red;\">(new)</span><br />\n第三&amp;四期民調結果POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1696271/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1696271/page/1</a><br />\n第二期民調結果POST <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1686054\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1686054</a><br />\n第一期民調結果POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1675545\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1675545</a><br />\n<br />\n眾籌link:  <a href=\"https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.collaction.hk%2Fproject%2Fstory%2F1209&d=VpJPAaQEVg4A3L06AjdBQIZnnstt8OVeiO3WagLZNiI%3D&h=d15a23d9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209</a><br />\n官方link (我們香港人計劃) :<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.pori.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pori.hk%2F&d=VpJPAaQEVg4A3L06AjdBQIZnnstt8OVeiO3WagLZNiI%3D&h=9f4ef64c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.pori.hk/</a><br />\n<br />\n(對唔住，咁危難時刻下我知而家仲叫大家課金可能好反感，但我相信兄弟爬山，各有各做，行得通就全力去做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)"},{"pid":"7eb49fe1c2326e9c638c304431f877c83ba6244c","tid":1727172,"uid":284517,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"6d4ad56add57008d6594dd947b80cfdb525ced6a","tid":1727172,"uid":182508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"52128cd35f3d07992d6dbef36e594b47d79c868e","tid":1727172,"uid":284517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T10:52:31.000Z","msg":"轉風向？<br />\n雨傘feel？<br />\n清路障？<br />\n而家收火？<br />\n<br />\n你地班人醒沒呀？五個月來我地失去左幾多手足啊！<br />\n<br />\n我懶得大篇理論。只問一句，你地初心係唔係忘記曬？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屌<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n純發洩 鍾意聽就聽 唔聽就算 反正我p牌一定屌我。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T10:57:52.